# Install Haskell base software

## Base Software from Hackage

### Cabal

* Go to the correct GHC directory with 

    switchghc X.Y.Z
    cp $HOME/Software/ghc-X.Y.Z

* Download newest version of *ghcup* from [https://www.haskell.org/ghcup](https://www.haskell.org/ghcup/) 

* Install correct cabal version with: (Note the blank between *cabal* and the version number.)

~~~
    ~/.ghcup/bin/ghcup install cabal U.V.W.Z --isolate $HOME/Software/ghc/bin
~~~

### Other base software

~~~
# Script to install different Haskell packages from Hackage 

cabal update

cabal install --overwrite-policy=always --installdir=$HOME/Software/ghc/bin --install-method=copy cabal-install 
cabal install --overwrite-policy=always --installdir=$HOME/Software/ghc/bin --install-method=copy alex 
cabal install --overwrite-policy=always --installdir=$HOME/Software/ghc/bin --install-method=copy happy  
cabal install --overwrite-policy=always --installdir=$HOME/Software/ghc/bin --install-method=copy hlint  
~~~
